review.reviewBody: Love there chicken balls (sweet&sour) just the right amount of crispness and you actually get a piece of chicken C3. And the bbq pork fried rice R4 is very good to best Chinese food in this area worth the money for sure
Always delish. And very generous.thanks to all the staff's effort and to the chef too.

Ordered 3x before with no issues- but was quite disappointed this time. I ordered just plain rice and an order of House Special fried rice, the latter was not mixed properly. There's soggy cabbage pieces and it lacked flavour.

P10. Pineapple Sweet & Sour Boneless Pork 咕噜肉 good, as usual. For the C13. Diced Chicken with Cashews 腰果鸡丁 I requested no MSG, and received this item with stronger garlic flavour than usual. And I'm not a garlic fan. :(

Everything arrived still hot! The D3. Steamed Pork Juicy Buns (10 Pieces) 小笼包  and M16. Stir Fried Chow Mein with Chicken 豉油皇炒面 were really good! And the portions are generous. Only 4 stars because the R5. Shrimp Fried Rice 虾仁炒饭 tasted a bit bland.
